      • editUserInfo

        public boolean editUserInfo(User user)
                     throws ServiceException,
                            UserInfoException
        Edits user profile info in a database if profile info is correct.
        An email must be "example@adress.com".
        Phone must be like "1234567890".
        All fields (surname, name, phone, email, passport ID, passport issued by, login) must be not empty.
        Specified by:
        editUserInfo in interface ProfileService
        Parameters:
        user - - user updated info. Only surname, name, phone, email, passport ID, passport issued by, login fields must be filled in.
        Returns:
